- network = local_assigns.fetch(:position_reliance_network)
- position = local_assigns.fetch(:position)
- components = network.components
= render "shared/cytoscape_dagre_scripts"

- if network.show_graph?
  - components.each_with_index do |component, index|
    - graph_id = "position-reliance-network-#{position.id}-#{index}"
    .assignment-accountability-flow-graph-wrapper{class: (index > 0) ? 'mt-4' : nil}
      - if components.size > 1
        %p.small.text-muted.mb-2 Connected flow #{index + 1}
      = render "shared/cytoscape/supply_flow_graph",
        elements: component.elements,
        root_node_ids: component.root_node_ids,
        export_filename: "position-reliance-network-#{position.id}-#{index + 1}",
        highlight_tiers: true,
        graph_id: graph_id,
        aria_label: "Position assignment supply reliance network"
  .d-flex.flex-wrap.gap-3.small.text-muted.mb-2.mt-3
    %span
      %span.d-inline-block.rounded.border.border-primary.border-3.me-1{style: "width: 14px; height: 14px; background-color: #cfe2ff; vertical-align: middle;"}
      Required on this position
    %span
      %span.d-inline-block.rounded.border.me-1{style: "width: 14px; height: 14px; background-color: #e7f1ff; border: 2px solid #6ea8fe !important; vertical-align: middle;"}
      Suggested on this position
    %span
      %span.d-inline-block.rounded.border.me-1{style: "width: 14px; height: 14px; background-color: #f1f3f5; border: 1px solid #ced4da !important; vertical-align: middle;"}
      One step away (supplier or consumer)
  %p.small.text-muted.mb-0
    %i.bi.bi-arrow-right.me-1
    Arrows show supply direction: an assignment on the left supplies results consumed by the assignment on the right.
    Click a node to open that assignment.
